strings: <voice_0x01001193><se_def>*: What's in! what are you doing together
<voice_0x01001194><se_def>*: You mean you don't know who will win?
<voice_0x01001195><se_high>*: C'mon, it goes without saying. Everything can end in a draw.
<voice_0x01001196><se_low>*: Does this mean that the casinos are closed? let me go!
<voice_0x01001197><se_def>Economy: Listen up everyone! as you can see The competition is a lottery, but I am sure that I am strong!
<voice_0x01001198><se_high>Install on PC: We both inherited property from our fathers.
<voice_0x01001199><se_def>Economy: To prove it We both got the Golding logo in the dragon's lair!
<voice_0x0100119A><se_low>*: This looks like a scar on Golding's hand.
<voice_0x0100119B><se_def>*: Yes, he bragged about it at the bar.
<voice_0x0100119C><se_high>Install on PC: I have good news for you as well. The casino will open its doors tomorrow!
<voice_0x0100119F><se_def>Economy: Finally, thank you for protecting your travel companions. But we're tired already
<voice_0x010011A0><se_def>Economy: Check into the villa as a guest today, pay tomorrow.
